info.description:
# Amsync Created with the aim that, anyone with basic knowledge of python, create any bot without much difficulty

# Installation ``` pip install Amsync ```

# Minimal example ```py from amsync import Bot, Msg bot = Bot('email', 'password', prefix='/') @bot.on() async def ready(): print('Ready') @bot.add() async def hi(m: Msg): await bot.send(f'Hi {m.nickname}') bot.run() ``` **[Incredible documentation to create beautiful bots](https://github.com/ellandor/Amsync/blob/main/docs/docs.md)**
info.name: Amsync
info.summary: An async library to easily create bots for the amino.
